nodes.text: Brother Lemcke was a male Mon Calamari who crowned Prince Lee-Char as the new King of Mon Cala at a special ceremony following the Battle of Mon Cala during the Clone Wars.

Brother Lemcke first appeared in the Star Wars: The Clone Wars episode "Prisoners," where he was voiced by Phil LaMarr, who also voiced Kit Fisto. While not named in the episode, he was identified in the accompanying StarWars.com episode guide.
